								<h3>Register Your Account.</h3>

							</div>

							<p>Sign up to become a member of the WeFund community and explore a variety of projects.</p>

						</div>

						<div class="col-lg-3 col-md-4 mt-5">

							<div class="feature-text">

								<div class="fbox-text color">2.</div>

								<h3>Discover Opportunities.</h3>

							</div>

							<p>Browse through a curated selection of projects and find those that inspire you.</p>

						</div>

						<div class="col-lg-3 col-md-4 mt-5">

